  "footer": "<br><br/><strong>NOTES:</strong>  For Venturers working on Scouts BSA requirements, replace \"troop\" with \"crew\" and \"Scoutmaster\" with \"Crew Advisor.\" For Sea Scouts working on Scouts BSA requirements, replace \"troop\" with \"ship\" and \"Scoutmaster\" with \"Skipper.\"\n<br><br>\n<sup>6</sup> Assistant patrol leader is not an approved position of responsibility for the Star, Life, or Eagle rank.<br>\n<br>\n<sup>7</sup> If your family does not have internet access at home AND you do not have ready internet access at school or another public place or via a mobile device, the Cyber Chip portion of this requirement may be waived by your Scoutmaster in consultation with your parent or guardian.<br><br>\n<sup>8</sup> If the board of review does not approve the Scout's advancement, the decision may be appealed in accordance with Guide to Advancement topic 8.0.4.0.",
